<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ900820-0124</DOCNO><DOCID>900820-0124.</DOCID><HL>   Newport to Repurchase Shares</HL><DATE>08/20/90</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION</SO><CO>   NEWP</CO><IN>BUYBACKS, REDEMPTIONS, SWAP OFFERS (BBK)</IN><LP>   FOUNTAIN VALLEY, Calif. -- Newport Corp. said itauthorized the repurchase of one million of its commonshares, or about 14% of the total outstanding, from time totime in the open market.   The repurchase program is in addition to aone-million-share buy-back program authorized in 1987. Sofar, the maker of laser instruments and parts and accessoriesfor the optics market has repurchased 774,000 shares underthe earlier buy-back program.</LP><TEXT/></DOC>